spec_data.Name: icewm-xdgmenu
spec_data.Description:
IceWM-xdgmenu generates static IceWM menu files from the existing
freedesktop.org .desktop files. Files are re-generated each time the
user logs-in.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 03 Aug 2017 11:46:41 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Automatically generate the main IceWM menu
